Author: jayrambling
Text: Florida. I don't think I'm eligible due to my age (22), if I'm not mistaken you need to be 24 or have dependents to be eligible for food stamps here.

Author: PoorLama
Text: What state are you in? You could be eligible for food assistance, I was receiving about $200 a month for food in my state when I was going to college. I'd check that avenue as well as if there are any food stamps in your area.
